name: HIRAGANA QUIZ｜ひらがなクイズ
description:
Let's memorize hiragana!

This MP4 can be used test your Hiragana memorization.
Play this MP4 on Looping with your phone / tablet / pc.
Press pause and guess what is the hiragana on display.
Press play again to randomize again.


This NFT is only available to those who managed to collect all 10 GIFs of the Hiragana Challenge.
